ie.gmit.Encoder

Class CoderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.Encoder.CoderFactory

  • public class CoderFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    A Gilani This class participates in the overall Factory pattern at play
    But i have defined few auxiliary methods so user can initialize the class and invoke methods
    This other system would fall under proxy pattern. I think but not sure as i am still trying to learn
    to differentiate the small difference between different patterns.
